Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:07.09,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:37.18,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:57.80,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:07.81,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.59,0:27:34.63,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.72,0:29:04.76,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking all this time about who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When Nana passed away, I felt so lonely and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to wonder why I even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I finally remembered.{really?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,was just a Shadow in that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, a Shadow living in that\N world awakened to human emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He made himself forget that he was a Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted people to like him,\N and that's how he came to look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shadows aren't allowed to stay in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when you meet Nana in Heaven, please apologize for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her I'm sorry I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:00:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}Wow! That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who meets all of the criteria must be here in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer must have a connection to both Konishi and Ms. Yamano...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as be in a position to observe our actions periodically to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, it must be someone who could approach your house without arousing suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We should review the information with everyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm returning to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I...{'m gay for you}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere deep down,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's more like I was jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were like me.{definitely gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from the city to the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be bored out of your mind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But as soon as you got here, you called your Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought us together. You're a real hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm proud of you...{nohomo}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about? {UH OH HE KNOWS}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a problem with how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I... {oh man oh god oh man oh god}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to look you in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to hit me! {what is this, k-on?}{what is this, BRS?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think out of everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be acknowledged by you the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a good one to knock out all this crap inside of me.{real gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to be equals, so c'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you wanted? {aww shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my second time punching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, this doesn't make us equals at all. {（´<_｀　）}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going around in circles on my own again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be equals if we both hit each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your punches are brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was seeing stars there for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's something that has struck me as strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame's diary had a detailed list of the people who had been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't include Kubo Mitsuo's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubo was a copycat killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He entered the TV on his own and killed King Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it really happen like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have acted under the assumption that Kubo "entered the TV on his own".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But we never actually confirmed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubo Mitsuo appeared on Midnight Channel, but if he didn't go there on his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the true culprit threw him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel better having talked to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, {life}partner!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's{\i0} the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something that's been bothering me about him for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the possibility isn't zero, then we can't rule him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he said he came to escort Ms. Yamano and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine he had contact with Konishi since she found Ms. Yamano's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that fit the criteria too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, it's Shirogane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with Amagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the people who went missing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,had been thrown into the TV by Namatame who was disguised as a deliveryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He came up to their front door and brazenly rang the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But only Kubo Mitsuo testified about what happened when he went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He blacked out in the police interrogation room when he turned himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned himself in? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle confirmed the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, no one took Kubo's confession seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubo was investigated by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you look so angry? {maybe because you killed his cousin idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako's room isn't around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dojima, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be up. You need your rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, where's Namatame?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame's already been relocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you so I could tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who authorized that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still more I need to ask him about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Those first two murders have been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,His motives are shaky,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and his alibi is rock solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this more of your "detective's intuition"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's already been relocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use hassling me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you kids should really get home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting in the way of police business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to confirm something with Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,With Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell us about the time Ms. Yamano went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporters were forcing their way into the inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so I went to serve as an undercover bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My memory's kinda hazy that far back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever speak with Konishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I did. She discovered the announcer's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But she didn't know much about it, so I only talked with her once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you learn anything about the warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I don't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I gave it to you to take down to the crime lab for processing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me you forgot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your accident was right after that, and what with one thing and another, it sorta slipped my mind.{>afterwards, what is this, BE?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what're you asking me all this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get to the station and report in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We know for certain now that the first two murders weren't Namatame's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, do you have any idea who that might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause we think it mighta been you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuckin' admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We already know Namatame's the one who put them all in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them all in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know something about the method behind the murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been fixated on something you once said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I finally understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recall when I read Namatame's diary at the scene of Dojima's accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the victims who survived and were never released to the public are written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I note that Mr. Morooka's address is absent from the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... Then that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How, I wonder, would that "settle" anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's odd you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the police had no idea there had been other attempted murders related to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet when Naoto read the list of names,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you raised no objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say to that, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I said I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear he ran this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. Where the hell'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, in my dream, you vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voices... I could hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard big brother's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if I'm just a Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something I can do!{the jp is lit. "something only i can do", dunno if you want to change it}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super foggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it even worse than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that means both our world and this world are going nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find his exact location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you here when we need you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You little... Where the hell were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Bad bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so late! Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bear-y sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured out a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff about me... and that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What's the problem with being a Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you now possess the power of Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it follow, then, that you must've developed an ego?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Teddie's practically human, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same as humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want you to go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you! I-I'm so glad I met you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to look for him too! Leave it to Fuzzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I'm getting something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thattaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are very persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, are you really the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our world will probably become just like this place soon enough anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, this place will be reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans will turn into Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who threw Ms. Yamano into the TV, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I could tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just called her to the lobby to ask her something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But then that woman went hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That isn't his real body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Adachi is somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The shopping district?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are somehow different this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like he's gained some strong power after coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say this world has taken a real shine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's given me everything I've ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the monsters don't attack me at all.\N Maybe they can tell we have the same goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Some powerful grizzly just popped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me, come and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see which of us this world favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on{senpai} and get Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,my inn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This shithole's been so boring that I spent every day glued to the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I had been secretly rooting for this woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And what'd you call me out here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All that talk about you having an affair and whatnot... It's all a lie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to explain myself to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't deny it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught my eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but it turns out you're just another worthless bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me call for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, shut up, shut up, shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you need to see what it's like to fear for your life. It'll get your head straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She fell in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So people can go completely inside!{that's what she said}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That happened in our lobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned about the Midnight Channel through some rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was pure coincidence that I touched the screen and discovered my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I burst out laughing when I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew right away this was going to be interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you tested it out on Yamano Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all. I'm a very sincere fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to punish the stupid bitch a little for betraying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn in Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi! Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaba will disappear into the fog soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This will become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, don't lose sight of Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Konishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you call me in for more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You were getting pretty cozy with that Namatame...{I'm working for someone named namatame lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's all cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep your little secret if you do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm not good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to deal with girls like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, high school girls today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This world's gone straight to shit.{The world is full of shit.}{TITLE DROP!}{sorry, gotta change it}{hey, fuck your shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on your knees and beg, and maybe I'll let you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd walk into a deathtrap like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be the best of the best, and instead they stick me in the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I got this sweet power to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it was dangerous inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I was trying to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bitches and whores{Mayumi and that high schooler} were just gold digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They got exactly what they deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What a chump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just tell you the real me is somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! What a tough bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This Shadow's on a completely different level from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This fog is going to drive everyone insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do to Namatame?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He called the police in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,just after they found that Saki girl's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... That's the pattern to the two deaths so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're seeing a girl in a kimono on that weird program, and you think she'll die too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame, do you seriously expect us to believe something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true! If there's any way the police can protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.21,0:22:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way the police
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to make a move based on a ridiculous story like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It does sound interesting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really wanna save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,why not do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, you could shelter her somewhere. Somewhere no one could find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where no one could find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Save her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the people who could've received Namatame's call, it ended up being me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was give him a little push.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The more people you guys saved, the more he'd kidnap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Both sides had the best of intentions, so the cycle would never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Because of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going bear-serk!{gotta fit in these bear puns while I still can}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You threw Kubo into the TV, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... he turned himself in pretty quick, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This was back when we didn't even know enough to issue a search warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But the other officers decided it was just a prank, so they pawned him off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think anyone would come forward and take the blame for all the incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we closed the case, Namatame would stop "saving" people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let that happen, or the game would be over.{I lost the game}{the game. you lost it}{goddamn you guys}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.65,0:24:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told the others I sent him home but threw him inside the TV instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.78,0:24:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The game would be over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.62,0:24:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your reason?{"ok"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta have some excitement in life, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.00,0:24:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you guys had to get involved and ruin my fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.34,0:24:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Kubo was arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone acted like he was the true culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't they see how badly he copied the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.51,0:24:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked out in the end, though, because good ol' Namatame kept saving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.73,0:25:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the guy started to develop\N some kinda messiah complex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.11,0:25:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.49,0:25:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm surprised you made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.41,0:25:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.58,0:25:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.75,0:25:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? No reason, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.63,0:25:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because I could, and it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.34,0:25:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was put people in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.84,0:25:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the world that really kills them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.05,0:25:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This world reflects people's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.14,0:25:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Which...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.37,0:25:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear... Does that mean the real culprits are everyone on the outside, including you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.44,0:25:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And aren't you high schoolers?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.03,0:25:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be studying instead of worrying about this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Study{party} hard, go to a good college, and marry a cute girl.{sounds like a plan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why get so worked up over things you can't change?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've got nothing better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.79,0:26:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all a bunch of lonely losers!{ronery roosers}{so badly want to put faggots, but... dame da}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.67,0:26:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the lonely one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.84,0:26:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.21,0:26:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so high and mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.72,0:26:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fucking cocky brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"We'll catch the true killer ourselves!"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.50,0:26:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.96,0:26:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.06,0:26:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit, my sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.23,0:26:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.02,0:26:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once your world is devoured,\N everyone'll turn into Shadows.{then the world will be one big happy place}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.78,0:26:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too late.{I prefer turning into tang, though}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.36,0:26:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I pity the fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.62,0:26:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Brats like you are so damned naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.12,0:26:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.00,0:26:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your very existence is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.62,0:26:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need annoying fucks like you in the new world.{KISS. KISS. KISS. KISS!!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.00,0:26:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.01,0:26:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.84,0:26:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could just leave you be, but you're like a plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.84,0:27:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you! Let's find out which of us this world favors!{end here and roll credits?}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.11,0:27:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Magatsu Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.24,0:27:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.87,0:27:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good boy and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.33,0:27:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.11,0:29:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality isn't a game!{more like "reality is a shitty game" amirite?}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.49,0:29:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a brat like you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.86,0:29:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the two worlds will collide!{oh fuck FFIX all over again}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.49,0:29:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.79,0:29:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
